q4.value:
Consensus in technology evaluation criteria and a firm’s technological performance have an interactive effect on investment such that 
(a) when a firm’s technological performance is unclear, the effect of evaluation criteria consensus is stronger/more positive than when the firm's technological performance is high or low; 
(b) when a firm's technological performance is high, the effect of evaluation criteria consensus is stronger/more positive than when the firm's technological performance is low.

